<h1 class="doc-page-title">COMPASS Overview</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">COMPASS (Compliance and Management Performance Assurance Support System) is a strategic delivery and compliance management platform for the Department for Education (DfE).</p>

<h2 id="what-is-compass">What is COMPASS?</h2>

<p>COMPASS provides comprehensive tools and features to support strategic oversight, compliance tracking, performance monitoring, and risk management across DfE products and services.</p>

<p>The platform enables teams to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Track and manage risks, actions, issues, and decisions (RAID)</li>
    <li>Monitor performance metrics at product and enterprise levels</li>
    <li>Assess compliance with DDaT functional standards</li>
    <li>Align activities with strategic objectives</li>
    <li>Generate reports and analytics for decision-making</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="key-capabilities">Key capabilities</h2>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card border-primary h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h5">Product governance</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive tracking and management of:</p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li><strong>Risks:</strong> Identify, assess, and mitigate potential threats</li>
                    <li><strong>Actions:</strong> Track and monitor action items and tasks</li>
                    <li><strong>Issues:</strong> Log and resolve problems as they arise</li>
                    <li><strong>Milestones:</strong> Monitor key deliverables and goals</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card border-success h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h5">Performance reporting</h3>
                <p>Track and report on product and enterprise performance:</p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>Product-level performance metrics</li>
                    <li>Enterprise-wide metrics and KPIs</li>
                    <li>Historical trend analysis</li>
                    <li>Custom reporting and dashboards</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card border-info h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h5">Compliance tracking</h3>
                <p>Monitor compliance with functional standards:</p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>DDaT functional standards assessments</li>
                    <li>Practice area evaluations</li>
                    <li>Theme-based compliance tracking</li>
                    <li>Criterion-level assessments</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card border-warning h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h5">Strategic alignment</h3>
                <p>Align activities with strategic objectives:</p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>Link products to strategic objectives</li>
                    <li>Track milestone progress</li>
                    <li>Monitor strategic goal achievement</li>
                    <li>Visualise strategic portfolios</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 id="platform-architecture">Platform architecture</h2>

<h3>Technology stack</h3>

<table class="table table-bordered">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Component</th>
            <th>Technology</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Framework</strong></td>
            <td>ASP.NET Core 8.0 (C#)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Database</strong></td>
            <td>Azure SQL Database (all environments)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Authentication</strong></td>
            <td>Azure Entra ID (Microsoft Identity Platform)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Frontend</strong></td>
            <td>GOV.UK Design System, AdminLTE</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Typography</strong></td>
            <td>Inter typeface (as per DfE design standards)</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Integration points</h3>

<p>COMPASS integrates with several DfE systems to provide a unified view:</p>

<table class="table table-bordered">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>System</th>
            <th>Integration purpose</th>
            <th>Data flow</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>FIPS CMS</strong></td>
            <td>Product catalogue and service information</td>
            <td>COMPASS fetches product data in real-time from FIPS CMS API</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Standards CMS</strong></td>
            <td>DDaT functional standards framework</td>
            <td>COMPASS can synchronise standards definitions and criteria</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Azure Entra ID</strong></td>
            <td>User authentication and staff directory</td>
            <td>COMPASS authenticates users and searches staff</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="user-roles">User roles and permissions</h2>

<p>COMPASS supports role-based access control with the following user types:</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6">Administrators</h3>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Full system access including:</strong></p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>User management</li>
                    <li>System settings configuration</li>
                    <li>Lookup table management</li>
                    <li>All RAID and reporting features</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6">Standard users</h3>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Access to core features including:</strong></p>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                    <li>View all products and reports</li>
                    <li>Create and edit RAID items for their products</li>
                    <li>Submit performance metrics</li>
                    <li>Conduct functional standards assessments</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 id="getting-started">Getting started</h2>

<p>To begin using COMPASS:</p>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Authenticate:</strong> Sign in using your DfE email address through Azure Entra ID</li>
    <li><strong>Navigate:</strong> Use the sidebar menu to access different sections of the platform</li>
    <li><strong>Search:</strong> Find products, risks, issues, and other items using the search functionality</li>
    <li><strong>Create:</strong> Add new RAID items, submit metrics, or conduct assessments</li>
    <li><strong>Report:</strong> View dashboards and reports to gain insights</li>
</ol>

